reviews.review_text: This place is very very close to the beach. Reasonable price range though it’s just close to the beach. A huge variety of cocktails available, and the food is tasty too. Tried their post roast and loved it. We also got a complimentary from the owner, butter garlic prawns which were super rich and amazing. Their steaks are a much try. Overall a very good place to visit.

A Must-Visit for Seafood Lovers in Goa!

It is a place for anyone who loves fresh and flavorful seafood. Their Goan seafood dishes are the highlight—perfectly spiced, fresh, and delicious. The butter garlic prawns and Goan fish curry are absolute must-tries!

The fully stocked bar and occasional live music make it a great place to unwind with friends or family. The staff is attentive and friendly, adding to the overall experience.

Highly recommend this spot for its great food, and authentic Goan charm!

Kentucky Seafood Restaurant offers a fantastic dining experience with its fresh and flavorful seafood in a warm, inviting atmosphere. The menu is diverse, featuring everything from classic fried fish to Cajun-style shrimp and oysters, all cooked to perfection. The service is friendly and attentive, making sure each guest feels welcome. The bar has a great selection of drinks, including craft beers and signature cocktails that perfectly complement the meal. Whether you're there for a casual night out or a special occasion, Kentucky Seafood Restaurant delivers on taste and quality. Highly recommend!
